description:
Polylend is a lending aggregator for Layer-2. We aim to optimize the lending process and provide earning opportunities on Polygon blockchain.
(1)It selects the best investment platform and optimizes financial services on Polygon blockchain ;
(2)It focuses on a larger spectrum of Layer-2 assets as collaterals (e.g., DeFi assets, NFTs, and other longtail coins);
(3)It makes the functions of collateral-repay and leverage accessible to mainstream users;
(4)It strives to connect lending pools from multi-chains and Rollup solutions.
We would aggregate all of the growing but fragmented lending markets to achieve the infinite expansion of liquidity and diversity in the tide of Layer-2.
